```

### Decision Tree Visualization
```
Need: 52.5 M Cable
    ↓
    ├─→ [Option 1] Redesign to ≤50M
    │   Cost: Design time (~$5K)
    │   Time: 1-2 weeks delay
    │   Ongoing: $0 waste
    │   ✓ Best long-term
    │
    ├─→ [Option 2] Buy 2 spools (100M)
    │   Cost: $500/unit (+100%)
    │   Time: No delay
    │   Ongoing: $250/unit waste
    │   ⚠️ Expensive ongoing
    │
    ├─→ [Option 3] Cut-to-length service
    │   Cost: $446/unit (+78%)
    │   Time: 4 week lead time
    │   Ongoing: $196/unit premium
    │   ⚠️ Supplier dependent
    │
    ├─→ [Option 4] Use splice/connector
    │   Cost: +$30/unit (connector + labor)
    │   Time: 1 week redesign
    │   Ongoing: Complexity + reliability risk
    │   ⚠️ Engineering compromise
    │
    └─→ [Option 5] In-house cutting
        Cost: $15K equipment + labor
        Time: 3 week setup
        Ongoing: Labor + QC cost
        ⚠️ Only viable at volume
```

