Manufacturing:
  ⏸️ Production delayed
  Impact: 1-4 weeks depending on decision

Finance:
  💰 Waste cost: $250/unit ongoing OR
  💰 One-time redesign: $5K
  Recommendation: Redesign = 20 unit payback

Project Management:
  📅 Schedule impact: 1-4 weeks
  Risk: High - critical path item
```

